Good to see you having fun.
now it's my turn!

516
00:50:13.501 --> 00:50:15.020
Guns in the bucket.

517
00:50:19.255 --> 00:50:20.056
And without any sudden moves.

518
00:50:20.878 --> 00:50:22.729
Frank! Gun in the bucket.

519
00:50:27.512 --> 00:50:28.546
And the rest. too.

520
00:50:31.086 --> 00:50:35.175
The kid. Malik. fine.
Calm. Now you. Anush.

521
00:50:38.214 --> 00:50:38.964
There.

522
00:50:43.305 --> 00:50:44.114
In the aquarium.

523
00:50:58.257 --> 00:50:59.424
Now leave us alone.

524
00:51:02.599 --> 00:51:04.110
Bastian. look at me.

525
00:51:06.540 --> 00:51:07.532
You know who I am?

526
00:51:09.526 --> 00:51:10.391
My name?

527
00:51:10.767 --> 00:51:11.759
Charlie Matei.

528
00:51:12.333 --> 00:51:14.119
Yes. I am Charlie Matei. and I'm going to kill you.

529
00:51:14.706 --> 00:51:16.983
I'll kill you in the open. it is a question of honor.

530
00:51:17.783 --> 00:51:19.558
I want you to know who will kill you.

531
00:51:19.801 --> 00:51:21.466
and why you died.

532
00:51:21.741 --> 00:51:23.510
You know why you will die. Bastian?

533
00:51:24.520 --> 00:51:25.045
Yes.

534
00:51:25.817 --> 00:51:29.840
When your killers face is hidden under a hood.
then it is murder without a signature. no class.

535
00:51:30.408 --> 00:51:31.365
Impersonal.

536
00:51:31.932 --> 00:51:32.941
You know the difference?

537
00:51:36.156 --> 00:51:37.249
You all understand?

538
00:51:38.406 --> 00:51:39.757
Because I will kill you all

539
00:51:41.110 --> 00:51:42.402
You're all in the queue.

540
00:51:43.083 --> 00:51:44.183
But not immediately. not right now.

541
00:51:44.792 --> 00:51:47.279
I want you to have time to
think about your sins.

542
00:51:47.849 --> 00:51:50.083
Day and night you will think about it.

543
00:51:50.692 --> 00:51:52.901
You'll have time to ask for forgiveness from your wives and children.

544
00:51:53.527 --> 00:51:55.420
To tell them why you will die.

545
00:51:56.109 --> 00:51:58.496
And you will wait for your death...

546
00:51:59.745 --> 00:52:05.405
It might be tomorrow. six months or a year.

547
00:52:06.161 --> 00:52:08.802
As long as I live. you will never be safe.

548
00:52:11.080 --> 00:52:14.897
And tell Zach that while I am alive
I will take my revenge on you all.

549
00:52:15.804 --> 00:52:16.562
Bastian!

550
00:52:17.021 --> 00:52:18.978
Charles! Please!

551
00:52:21.282 --> 00:52:22.983
Take one last look at the time.

552
00:52:26.064 --> 00:52:27.532
Happy Birthday. Bastiaan!

553
00:52:45.753 --> 00:52:48.274
Leave it alone! Leave it alone!

554
00:52:50.034 --> 00:52:51.897
Do not touch me! Leave me alone!

555
00:52:54.092 --> 00:52:55.527
Get away from me!

556
00:52:55.983 --> 00:52:56.699
Listen to me!

557
00:52:56.735 --> 00:53:00.211
I don't want to listen to you!
I don't want to be here in Avignon.

558
00:53:01.020 --> 00:53:02.720
Your father said that its safer here!

559
00:53:02.757 --> 00:53:06.312
Well. of course! My father said that!
I'm not going to do what he fucking says!

560
00:53:06.813 --> 00:53:07.881
I am going back to Marseilles!

561
00:53:09.062 --> 00:53:09.967
stop it!

562
00:53:10.349 --> 00:53:14.116
You are the most intelligent? You think
that you understand me better than anyone. right?

563
00:53:14.274 --> 00:53:15.117
That's not fair!

564
00:53:15.154 --> 00:53:17.176
My mother is dying
I want to be with her!

565
00:53:18.991 --> 00:53:21.058
Well. what can you do to stop me ?

566
00:53:21.626 --> 00:53:24.934
Nothing compared with what they will do to you if they catch you.

567
00:53:25.580 --> 00:53:27.281
Same ss they did with your father..

568
00:53:31.844 --> 00:53:34.887
My child! it's all so very difficult.

569
00:53:35.705 --> 00:53:37.403
Enough. do not!

570
00:53:38.380 --> 00:53:41.032
Enough! Go. Come to me.

571
00:53:42.641 --> 00:53:43.525
All is well.

572
00:53:57.656 --> 00:53:58.780
Our dear son.

573
00:53:59.182 --> 00:54:02.148
Forgive me son.
I went to get flowers from trumanyek

574
00:54:02.688 --> 00:54:05.265
He has beautiful roses.
but he is such a moron.

575
00:54:06.281 --> 00:54:09.650
once everything
was just for you!

576
00:54:09.686 --> 00:54:11.183
devoted to you

577
00:54:11.798 --> 00:54:13.231
Do you remember these days. eh?

578
00:54:13.748 --> 00:54:14.648
You know why people have to die?

579
00:54:19.341 --> 00:54:21.193
Because I have no answer.

580
00:54:21.433 --> 00:54:23.333
After the death of my son. I lost my head.

581
00:54:23.642 --> 00:54:25.868
So. I am not myself after the death of Karim.

582
00:54:26.658 --> 00:54:30.193
I'm sorry that it happened. but it
was not my idea. I just watched.

583
00:54:33.599 --> 00:54:34.634
I am unarmed.

584
00:54:34.807 --> 00:54:40.495
I am not in the habit of killing....Not my rules to kill unarmed
people. but sometimes rules can change.

585
00:55:01.049 --> 00:55:04.224
I ask you. please. quiet!
Monsieur Zakia has a migraine!

586
00:55:04.591 --> 00:55:06.458
Might become a fit! Come.

587
00:55:09.115 --> 00:55:10.559
Light it is kept low..

588
00:55:10.595 --> 00:55:13.884
Bright lights could start a belter
of a headache.

589
00:55:14.309 --> 00:55:15.896
Especially. if it's noisy

590
00:55:19.529 --> 00:55:20.404
No. only you.

591
00:55:26.066 --> 00:55:26.776
Come!

592
00:55:28.372 --> 00:55:28.948
Come.

593
00:55:33.088 --> 00:55:33.770
Le Bekyu.

594
00:55:45.180 --> 00:55:49.538
Goldman. Goldman. somewhere
I've heard that name.

595
00:55:49.575 --> 00:55:51.124
I can not now remember exactly.

596
00:55:51.555 --> 00:55:53.197
A police officer with that name...

597
00:55:53.234 --> 00:55:56.090
My husband. He was killed by people.
gunned down because he was a cop.

598
00:55:56.127 --> 00:55:59.392
He was involved in an investigation. maybe getting close to something

599
00:55:59.393 --> 00:56:00.434
No proof...you understand Mr Zakia..

600
00:56:02.729 --> 00:56:03.370
Of Course.

601
00:56:03.986 --> 00:56:05.694
I am interested Charlie Matei.

602
00:56:06.235 --> 00:56:08.920
I believe you think
that he killed Papalardo?

603
00:56:09.769 --> 00:56:13.427
You know and have worked with Matei.
you know how he thinks.

604
00:56:13.968 --> 00:56:15.968
After the shooting he became paranoid.

605
00:56:16.197 --> 00:56:18.063
Always looking for an excuse to annoy me.

606
00:56:18.730 --> 00:56:20.305
You see. what has happened!

607
00:56:21.430 --> 00:56:24.275
He is sick I tell you..People love it because I
do not know what he will do.

608
00:56:26.026 --> 00:56:29.442
I remember once he got mad ..
took a plane to Algeria.

609
00:56:29.851 --> 00:56:31.494
Went looking for someone who owed him money.

610
00:56:32.086 --> 00:56:34.307
We found him hiding in the countryside.
scared..

611
00:56:34.963 --> 00:56:38.163
He starved him for a week and then buried him alive.

612
00:56:38.940 --> 00:56:40.165
He's crazy. believe me!

613
00:56:40.202 --> 00:56:41.957
But you never reported this to the police.

614
00:56:41.994 --> 00:56:43.099
And what would that change?

615
00:56:43.135 --> 00:56:45.875
You know that he killed Papalardo.
and what are you doing about it?

616
00:56:46.123 --> 00:56:47.083
Sit idly by.

617
00:56:48.593 --> 00:56:51.335
Do not worry. Mr Zakia.
that's how a migraine begins.

618
00:56:51.372 --> 00:56:52.727
I'm not worried. I am calm.

619
00:56:53.603 --> 00:56:56.812
But if you continue to stand idly by
this will nn-nn end badly!

620
00:56:56.848 --> 00:56:58.002
Are you threatening me?

621
00:57:00.735 --> 00:57:02.878
Monsieur Zakia. we are perfectly aware
and know who is who.

622
00:57:03.796 --> 00:57:07.313
I am in the police. I am required to catch criminals ...

623
00:57:07.349 --> 00:57:09.446
Once you get to the bigger fish. its a brick wall

624
00:57:10.764 --> 00:57:12.724
I do not have any cause to question matei.

625
00:57:12.760 --> 00:57:16.615
I Don't have the budget to investigate.
It's not normal!

626
00:57:19.424 --> 00:57:20.365
You do not like me?

627
00:57:21.214 --> 00:57:23.480
I'm at work I do not show emotions.

628
00:57:28.030 --> 00:57:31.763
You see. What I'm asking
from you is not impossible.

629
00:57:32.396 --> 00:57:35.563
I know a young widow with a small
child cannot live easily.

630
00:57:35.870 --> 00:57:37.171
How do you know about the child?

631
00:57:38.063 --> 00:57:39.238
I just assumed.

632
00:57:39.952 --> 00:57:42.268
If I can help you
somehow ...

633
00:57:42.305 --> 00:57:46.510
It's trite. but sometimes a material
assistance may help the situation.

634
00:57:48.087 --> 00:57:53.271
And when I advise you to pay more
attention to Matei..I do not believe this is an act of squealing.

635
00:57:54.114 --> 00:57:57.356
I would call this kind. sincere
friendly advice. a public duty.

636
00:58:00.455 --> 00:58:02.614
I earn my own bread without outside help.

637
00:58:05.798 --> 00:58:07.880
You want to persuade me to
start an investigation?

638
00:58:08.399 --> 00:58:09.206
I'll think about it.

639
00:58:10.274 --> 00:58:11.123
Or maybe not!

640
00:58:12.542 --> 00:58:13.717
See You around. monsieur Zakia.

641
00:59:55.993 --> 00:59:56.777
Hey. keep quiet!

642
00:59:57.918 --> 00:59:58.462
Yes.

643
00:59:59.623 --> 01:00:00.297
Do not lose him

644
01:00:01.569 --> 01:00:02.327
You lot. with me!

645
01:00:14.325 --> 01:00:15.067
Are you hungry?

646
01:00:26.900 --> 01:00:28.932
You love meat with olive oil.

647
01:00:30.825 --> 01:00:32.317
Thank you for the company.

648
01:00:36.697 --> 01:00:37.238
Like it?

649
01:00:40.203 --> 01:00:43.185
There is no time right now. but when all this is
over. I'll do it then.

650
01:00:44.051 --> 01:00:44.785
The Corsair!

651
01:00:46.368 --> 01:00:47.785
I'll call her Corsair.

652
01:00:48.375 --> 01:00:49.476
Romantic. yes?

653
01:00:50.799 --> 01:00:52.934
My son Anatole. too. loves the sea.

654
01:00:54.250 --> 01:00:56.065
You know. it's so quiet and peaceful

655
01:00:57.426 --> 01:01:01.711
Any minute it can all change. but when you sit
and just look at these waves...

656
01:01:03.375 --> 01:01:04.902
Life seems ideal.

657
01:01:15.303 --> 01:01:16.962
I had a dog once. alcoholic.

658
01:01:17.955 --> 01:01:21.837
Once I gave it a slurp. a mouthful;
she was full of tricks then!

659
01:01:22.193 --> 01:01:23.226
Just to get even.

660
01:01:23.787 --> 01:01:25.613
Alcohol made her aggressive.

661
01:01:26.262 --> 01:01:27.908
So no. I will not give you.

662
01:01:28.874 --> 01:01:29.715
Do you understand me?

663
01:01:57.931 --> 01:01:58.456
Charlie!

664
01:02:00.629 --> 01:02:01.069
Charlie!

665
01:02:12.530 --> 01:02:13.178
Charlie!

666
01:02:46.409 --> 01:02:47.354
Something wrong?

667
01:02:49.072 --> 01:02:50.010
You frightened me.

668
01:02:51.901 --> 01:02:52.844
Why did you come?

669
01:02:53.052 --> 01:02:53.877
To see you.

670
01:02:54.287 --> 01:02:55.752
Zack has gone fucking crazy.

671
01:02:56.135 --> 01:02:59.087
They smashed the hell out of your house
looking for your mother.

672
01:03:00.150 --> 01:03:02.160
They are looking everywhere for me. and you
fucking well brought them to me.

673
01:03:02.196 --> 01:03:05.552
I care about Klatide.
I cannot sit idly by!

674
01:03:06.194 --> 01:03:07.651
She needs medical care. and I ...

675
01:03:08.126 --> 01:03:08.986
They are already here.

676
01:03:14.059 --> 01:03:15.444
On the pier by boat. run!

677
01:03:17.310 --> 01:03:18.278
It's not possible..

678
01:03:24.652 --> 01:03:26.022
Yeah we will...don't dawdle..run!

679
01:04:19.709 --> 01:04:20.401
Hello mate!

680
01:05:00.737 --> 01:05:01.598
Do not lose him..

681
01:05:13.310 --> 01:05:13.996
Faster!

682
01:05:16.958 --> 01:05:17.824
Come On!

683
01:06:15.167 --> 01:06:16.979
Shit! Wank! Bollocks! Arseholes!

684
01:06:22.105 --> 01:06:23.937
Monsieur. you hear us? What happened?

685
01:06:45.049 --> 01:06:51.223
Matin. I want Charlie. I'll ask you.
and you'll Tell me okay?

686
01:06:55.581 --> 01:06:57.090
Otherwise it's all over for you matey..

687
01:07:06.157 --> 01:07:08.457
Give my regards to Klatide..

688
01:07:13.856 --> 01:07:16.208
You are either at the hospital or in prison
and always bored M. Matei?

689
01:07:16.608 --> 01:07:18.219
Neither one nor the other. I came to see you!

690
01:07:20.982 --> 01:07:22.299
I wanted to see you.

691
01:07:22.998 --> 01:07:26.066
You want to confess to the murder of Anji
Papalardo and Bastian Paolini?

692
01:07:27.025 --> 01:07:27.557
murdered?

693
01:07:27.790 --> 01:07:29.150
They are dead?

694
01:07:29.186 --> 01:07:31.898
Shot through the heart and head. It's your signature?

695
01:07:33.606 --> 01:07:34.680
My hands are tied.

696
01:07:35.602 --> 01:07:37.920
So the signature ...
Do not believe everything you hear.

697
01:07:37.957 --> 01:07:41.203
I also know you have sent your family away while you do your thing.

698
01:07:42.075 --> 01:07:45.016
You killed those two people and you continue to take revenge.

699
01:07:46.201 --> 01:07:47.417
Everyone in the world takes revenge.

700
01:07:47.893 --> 01:07:49.242
For his family. for children.

701
01:07:49.634 --> 01:07:50.960
And sometimes even for enemies.

702
01:07:51.352 --> 01:07:52.869
Maybe you do not have enemies?

703
01:07:52.905 --> 01:07:53.959
Not as many as you

704
01:07:54.920 --> 01:07:56.353
we have a common enemy?

705
01:07:58.308 --> 01:07:59.877
I was a victim of reputation.

706
01:07:59.913 --> 01:08:01.516
You got what you deserved.

707
01:08:01.942 --> 01:08:04.883
Oh no. the reality is more prosaic than that.

708
01:08:04.920 --> 01:08:06.453
I am an ordinary pensioner.

709
01:08:06.490 --> 01:08:07.370
Retired!

710
01:08:07.576 --> 01:08:08.277
You work?

711
01:08:08.314 --> 01:08:09.440
I work hard.

712
01:08:10.114 --> 01:08:14.666
Chief bottle washer. artistic director. cat breeder. does it matter. I pay my taxes

713
01:08:15.341 --> 01:08:18.549
And what was it that entered the minds of Anji Papalardo
and Bastin Paolini?

714
01:08:19.646 --> 01:08:20.747
They called on the Lord.

715
01:08:20.784 --> 01:08:23.326
Yes. recently the Lord
encourages many to join him.

716
01:08:23.873 --> 01:08:25.523
They encroached on your life.

717
01:08:26.056 --> 01:08:28.106
If you think I killed them arrest me.

718
01:08:28.530 --> 01:08:29.878
I have no evidence.

719
01:08:30.489 --> 01:08:33.031
Divine Justice then.

720
01:08:33.067 --> 01:08:34.340
Are you a believer!

721
01:08:35.431 --> 01:08:35.991
must be..

722
01:08:39.293 --> 01:08:42.308
Among your attackers there was one.
who did not wish your death.

723
01:08:43.351 --> 01:08:45.519
He put a whole clip
past you. just to the left.

724
01:08:45.555 --> 01:08:46.544
You're Crazy.

725
01:08:46.580 --> 01:08:47.232
No.

726
01:08:47.833 --> 01:08:50.443
His bullets flew close. but he
specifically shot past you to the left. no doubt.

727
01:08:50.651 --> 01:08:52.285
rounds all grouped closely.

728
01:08:52.994 --> 01:08:54.944
So. of those five - one was on your side.

729
01:08:54.981 --> 01:08:55.821
There were five?

730
01:08:56.330 --> 01:08:59.029
Eight actually. Five to shoot you.
one along for the ride and two drivers.

731
01:08:59.066 --> 01:09:02.889
I promise you. next time a load of geezers try to kill me
I'll pay more attention

732
01:09:10.542 --> 01:09:11.324
How do you know!

733
01:09:17.963 --> 01:09:19.714
I wanted to eat the rabbit with mustard!

734
01:09:19.750 --> 01:09:21.181
Its wasn't on the menu. Mama.

735
01:09:21.218 --> 01:09:22.012
Yes it was?

736
01:09:22.048 --> 01:09:23.364
Anyway. we had lunch.

737
01:09:24.715 --> 01:09:25.507
Very sorry.

738
01:09:26.665 --> 01:09:28.958
Anyway. I wanted rabbit with mustard!

739
01:09:28.995 --> 01:09:30.859
Mom. next time I'll take you somewhere with rabbit?

740
01:09:35.843 --> 01:09:36.551
No. Not now!

741
01:09:40.926 --> 01:09:45.511
Dont' argue! I still want rabbit with mustard!

742
01:10:55.821 --> 01:10:56.791
I'm glad you made it!

743
01:11:07.650 --> 01:11:08.636
Good evening. Frank!

744
01:11:23.452 --> 01:11:24.470
Come. come!

745
01:11:24.936 --> 01:11:28.262
let me introduce to you! Pierre Dyubuar!
You heard of him.

746
01:11:28.262 --> 01:11:30.212
Member of the Extraordinary Council of the Interior.

747
01:11:30.248 --> 01:11:32.137
This is Senator Charles battery.

748
01:11:33.150 --> 01:11:36.390
Vice-President of the Regional Council.
Very important bird!

749
01:11:37.974 --> 01:11:39.403
My friend Aurelio Rampaul!

750
01:11:42.705 --> 01:11:44.789
You shot my foot! You sick twat!

751
01:11:45.846 --> 01:11:47.831
I want a little chat with you. man.

752
01:11:48.281 --> 01:11:49.185
You fucking shit!

753
01:11:49.643 --> 01:11:52.743
Bravo. Frank. I'll tell your friends.
that you became a hero!

754
01:12:00.277 --> 01:12:02.143
Damn! Where is he hanging around at?

755
01:12:02.573 --> 01:12:03.326
Call him!

756
01:12:03.760 --> 01:12:05.011
I'm bleeding to death..

757
01:12:05.156 --> 01:12:06.908
Don't worry. you've got five litres of blood left.

758
01:12:11.578 --> 01:12:12.651
Listen carefully Frank.

759
01:12:13.512 --> 01:12:19.021
When you load of cunts tried to kill me. you were in the car park with
Bastian. Papalardo. Fantaroza. Malik.
Marvelus Jr.. and Zach.

760
01:12:19.545 --> 01:12:20.603
who was the eighth?

761
01:12:22.465 --> 01:12:22.906
No answer.

762
01:12:24.142 --> 01:12:24.717
He's a twat.

763
01:12:24.754 --> 01:12:25.321
yes.

764
01:12:25.763 --> 01:12:26.821
So go find him!

765
01:12:26.858 --> 01:12:27.522
All right.

766
01:12:28.912 --> 01:12:31.096
When I got there he was already there with Zak.

767
01:12:31.368 --> 01:12:32.710
I swear. I do not know who he is.

768
01:12:32.746 --> 01:12:34.134
I'm not fucking lying Charlie..

769
01:12:34.910 --> 01:12:37.712
You expect me to believe you turned up for the job. saw a stranger ...

770
01:12:37.749 --> 01:12:40.586
And didn't even ask
Who he was?

771
01:12:41.253 --> 01:12:44.013
I asked him.
but Fantaroza sent me out.

