1032
01:36:29.258 --> 01:36:32.815
Aurelio Rampaul's people all dead.
Well. there are five dead and one severely wounded.

1033
01:36:33.480 --> 01:36:34.303
A weapon?

1034
01:36:34.339 --> 01:36:35.881
No. before our arrival. everything was removed.

1035
01:36:35.917 --> 01:36:36.886
nothing..

1036
01:36:36.923 --> 01:36:37.639
Almost.

1037
01:36:38.346 --> 01:36:39.746
It was in the pocket of Aurelio.

1038
01:37:05.743 --> 01:37:06.357
Sonya

1039
01:37:09.248 --> 01:37:10.018
Sonya

1040
01:37:11.261 --> 01:37:12.039
The kids!

1041
01:37:48.406 --> 01:37:51.749
He helped me a lot. He is not only
the Revered healer.

1042
01:37:52.760 --> 01:37:55.810
He warns the faithful
of approaching death.

1043
01:37:56.701 --> 01:37:59.569
He knocks on the bed of those left to die for three days.

1044
01:38:00.880 --> 01:38:02.664
And to you he did not come?

1045
01:38:02.701 --> 01:38:04.287
What have you done to my family?

1046
01:38:05.657 --> 01:38:07.837
I wouldn't worry about your family.

1047
01:38:09.898 --> 01:38:11.224
I want to understand the ...

1048
01:38:11.260 --> 01:38:11.908
Understand?

1049
01:38:12.505 --> 01:38:13.724
What do you want to understand?

1050
01:38:20.100 --> 01:38:21.120
Why did you do it?

1051
01:38:23.942 --> 01:38:24.624
Business.

1052
01:38:25.219 --> 01:38:26.704
I'm not talking about business.

1053
01:38:27.079 --> 01:38:29.127
We vowed to be friends until death.
Remember?

1054
01:38:30.950 --> 01:38:32.172
I never said that

1055
01:38:32.720 --> 01:38:34.353
We vowed to be friends to death!

1056
01:38:34.737 --> 01:38:36.997
We grew up together.
never apart!

1057
01:38:37.033 --> 01:38:38.642
You grow old and are confused!

1058
01:38:39.285 --> 01:38:40.933
You old man! Weakling!

1059
01:38:41.609 --> 01:38:42.601
Always criticising. moaning..

1060
01:38:43.055 --> 01:38:44.966
And I continue to fight.

1061
01:38:45.127 --> 01:38:47.212
There are boundaries
for which I have respect

1062
01:38:47.249 --> 01:38:50.292
What crap? so. you have morals.
Very original.

1063
01:38:50.328 --> 01:38:51.836
Morality is not original.

1064
01:38:52.245 --> 01:38:53.294
It is not all pleasant.

1065
01:38:53.331 --> 01:38:54.625
You think you're different. Charlie?

1066
01:38:55.150 --> 01:38:56.032
You think you're better?

1067
01:38:56.877 --> 01:38:57.990
But we're the same.

1068
01:38:58.247 --> 01:39:01.242
You're not better than me. We're both on the same track

1069
01:39:01.633 --> 01:39:05.049
We go about it differently.
there is no code of honour!

1070
01:39:05.371 --> 01:39:07.980
We are the same! We both have hands in blood!
And the blood does not wash off!

1071
01:39:08.269 --> 01:39:10.868
And you will always be
on the wrong side of the law.

1072
01:39:11.208 --> 01:39:12.587
So. don't preach to me..

1073
01:39:12.623 --> 01:39:16.317
Kill me. because I lost.
But not in the name of your morality

1074
01:39:17.591 --> 01:39:19.035
I want to end it peacefully.

1075
01:39:19.072 --> 01:39:20.046
I would too.

1076
01:39:20.728 --> 01:39:24.063
But i had to kill you.
because of your selective morality!

1077
01:39:25.588 --> 01:39:27.034
Racket yes. drugs no!

1078
01:39:27.384 --> 01:39:28.860
Friends. but not family members.

1079
01:39:29.649 --> 01:39:30.803
Kill. but not cops!

1080
01:39:31.275 --> 01:39:33.211
And this is all bullshit.

1081
01:39:33.987 --> 01:39:35.770
The evil is in us. no half measures

1082
01:39:37.502 --> 01:39:38.657
Do not agree with me?

1083
01:39:39.505 --> 01:39:41.646
Do you want to kill me
because you cannot stand the truth.

1084
01:39:45.936 --> 01:39:47.665
No. because you betrayed me.

1085
01:39:50.819 --> 01:39:51.441
Come on then

1086
01:39:52.338 --> 01:39:53.174
What are you waiting for?

1087
01:40:01.891 --> 01:40:03.975
Do not think for a long time. otherwise you can't make up your mind.

1088
01:40:38.573 --> 01:40:41.388
We grow old in different ways.
but I don't fuck about like you!

1089
01:40:42.289 --> 01:40:43.973
And pity sometimes kills!

1090
01:40:46.376 --> 01:40:48.825
For three days before you recovered?
I was dying to live and let live!

1091
01:40:48.862 --> 01:40:51.153
And you'll be sorry that I didn't kill you.

1092
01:40:52.957 --> 01:40:54.056
Beg for your life..

1093
01:40:56.715 --> 01:40:59.266
Ask me. Charlie. beg me!

1094
01:41:00.479 --> 01:41:01.131
Zac!

1095
01:41:02.189 --> 01:41:03.096
Yes. Charlie?

1096
01:41:05.929 --> 01:41:07.488
You're the biggest bastard in the world.

1097
01:41:14.898 --> 01:41:16.702
I said. beg me!

1098
01:41:17.654 --> 01:41:18.409
Please!

1099
01:41:26.004 --> 01:41:28.041
The police do not move!

1100
01:41:28.077 --> 01:41:30.444
Back! Drop your weapon!

1101
01:41:30.481 --> 01:41:32.362
Weapons on the floor! Do not move!

1102
01:41:41.147 --> 01:41:42.695
Tony Zakia. you're fucking nicked mate.

1103
01:41:43.033 --> 01:41:44.500
You will be detained.

1104
01:41:44.536 --> 01:41:47.713
You are accused of fraud
illegal operations.

1105
01:41:47.750 --> 01:41:50.094
Wankers! He came to kill me!

1106
01:41:50.615 --> 01:41:51.407
Motherfucker!

1107
01:41:53.022 --> 01:42:00.092
The fall of Tony Zakia has resonated
around Marseilles. indeed. the whole of France.

1108
01:42:02.707 --> 01:42:07.319
Our city is finally moving into a new
era. which is to your merit Captain.

1109
01:42:07.733 --> 01:42:09.635
Thank's to your excellent service and determination.

1110
01:42:10.749 --> 01:42:14.583
The Minister of Internal Affairs will come to personally
congratulate us.

1111
01:42:14.736 --> 01:42:19.268
So. I think that on this occasion
you will forget our differences ...

1112
01:42:19.304 --> 01:42:21.951
And celebrate my achievements in the fight against
crime.

1113
01:42:22.646 --> 01:42:24.730
I'm not sure I understand you.
sir.

1114
01:42:24.730 --> 01:42:26.315
Then I put it more precisely.

1115
01:42:27.075 --> 01:42:32.047
An internal investigation revealed that
After her husband's death you have an
alcohol dependence.

1116
01:42:32.635 --> 01:42:35.559
You  were addicted to gambling

1117
01:42:36.708 --> 01:42:41.609
In addition to this. you actively
participated in the escape Charlie Matei.

1118
01:42:42.468 --> 01:42:46.150
And you sanctioned
using resources improperly.

1119
01:42:46.790 --> 01:42:52.276
If the minister should drop by for an unexpected
visit. you'll be queen for the day ...

1120
01:42:52.312 --> 01:42:58.654
But if you agree that Matei was my case.
these matters will remain between us

1121
01:43:01.948 --> 01:43:05.912
It will be my pleasure. I'm going to fight
criminals on your behalf.

1122
01:43:05.948 --> 01:43:07.008
Thank's for the favour.

1123
01:43:13.565 --> 01:43:15.173
Finally. Mr. Director.

1124
01:43:15.210 --> 01:43:15.929
Yes.

1125
01:43:21.700 --> 01:43:22.807
This is just between us.

1126
01:43:26.491 --> 01:43:29.327
You cops are constantly looking at me for
crimes I did not commit.

1127
01:43:29.363 --> 01:43:31.194
And for what I have done...are not looking.

1128
01:43:32.131 --> 01:43:35.178
You say that we are all idiots
and you. cops are clearly no better.

1129
01:43:37.519 --> 01:43:39.039
So you were not active in Marseilles?

1130
01:43:39.583 --> 01:43:40.246
No.

1131
01:43:42.503 --> 01:43:45.076
And you're not involved
the murder of Malik?

1132
01:43:45.112 --> 01:43:45.781
No.

1133
01:43:48.436 --> 01:43:50.040
And you do not know
Who could have done it?

1134
01:43:50.877 --> 01:43:51.457
No.

1135
01:43:57.276 --> 01:43:58.658
You know this gun?

1136
01:44:01.389 --> 01:44:03.525
No. I do not know.

1137
01:44:04.263 --> 01:44:05.904
Had your fingerprints on it?

1138
01:44:09.811 --> 01:44:10.645
Don't know how.

1139
01:44:13.465 --> 01:44:15.594
Maybe I touched it
in a weapon shop.

1140
01:44:16.626 --> 01:44:17.369
In  a store?

1141
01:44:18.942 --> 01:44:20.563
Do you have a firearms permit Mr Matei?

1142
01:44:20.653 --> 01:44:24.368
No. Do I need one to look at guns in stores?

1143
01:44:26.027 --> 01:44:27.978
And where did you get the weapon you had
when you were arrested?

1144
01:44:28.336 --> 01:44:29.554
In the house of Monsieur Zakii.

1145
01:44:33.398 --> 01:44:36.344
Tony Zakia says that you
broke into his house to kill him.

1146
01:44:37.297 --> 01:44:40.923
I broke in? he invited me. We're old friends.

1147
01:44:48.054 --> 01:44:49.965
Read this statement and sign.

1148
01:44:51.843 --> 01:44:56.186
You are accused of illegal possession of weapons.
as well as the breaking and entering of private
property.

1149
01:44:56.803 --> 01:44:58.823
But for your lawyer it's child's play.

1150
01:45:20.974 --> 01:45:21.782
I'm free?

1151
01:45:23.942 --> 01:45:28.364
The examination confirmed the testimony of
Yasmin. The killer was right-handed.

1152
01:45:41.798 --> 01:45:45.483
But Zakia. he will be charged
with a variety of offences.

1153
01:45:46.720 --> 01:45:49.933
And by law he will receive the maximum
sentence.

1154
01:45:52.042 --> 01:45:54.641
I have fulfilled my duty.
it's my job.

1155
01:45:56.375 --> 01:45:57.812
But as a human ...

1156
01:46:01.121 --> 01:46:03.007
I regret that I got there early.

1157
01:46:04.377 --> 01:46:09.292
You do not feel as much regret
as I. but along with you. it's a weak spot.

1158
01:46:09.890 --> 01:46:10.981
This is family.

1159
01:46:16.197 --> 01:46:18.063
Hopefully
we'll never see each other again.

1160
01:46:28.012 --> 01:46:31.422
Zakia told you who was
Eighth assailant?

1161
01:46:34.332 --> 01:46:35.003
No.

1162
01:47:13.068 --> 01:47:14.402
I brought what you asked for.

1163
01:47:19.819 --> 01:47:21.461
Christelle and the children are waiting for you at home.

1164
01:47:21.896 --> 01:47:23.255
Karim's parents arrived.

1165
01:47:23.731 --> 01:47:25.836
I would like to talk to you alone.

1166
01:47:26.158 --> 01:47:26.859
sure..

1167
01:47:29.111 --> 01:47:29.865
Where?

1168
01:47:30.988 --> 01:47:32.349
Drive. I'll say.

1169
01:47:55.770 --> 01:47:57.481
Strange thing I do.

1170
01:48:00.316 --> 01:48:04.441
If you decide to stay. be sure
that sooner or later someone will knock on
door ...

1171
01:48:04.477 --> 01:48:07.321
To avenge his father.
son. or uncle.

1172
01:48:10.999 --> 01:48:12.416
You're cursed to live with it.

1173
01:48:14.775 --> 01:48:15.861
And suffer.

1174
01:48:18.256 --> 01:48:20.325
And the bloodshed did not dry out.

1175
01:48:39.267 --> 01:48:40.657
This is where they tried to kill you.

1176
01:48:45.235 --> 01:48:45.927
They?

1177
01:48:45.928 --> 01:48:46.970
You think I'm fucking stupid Martin?

1178
01:48:51.346 --> 01:48:52.157
Charlie.

1179
01:48:54.256 --> 01:48:57.652
Zack broke me like crazy.
He said that I would be set for life.

1180
01:48:58.082 --> 01:49:00.901
I refused. but he put
a gun in my hand.

1181
01:49:01.517 --> 01:49:04.195
I even could not imagine
that he could do it to you!

1182
01:49:04.890 --> 01:49:06.606
And when I realized it was true. it was too late.

1183
01:49:29.196 --> 01:49:30.232
But I did not shoot at you!

1184
01:49:31.391 --> 01:49:32.781
I was aiming away from you. I swear!

1185
01:49:33.292 --> 01:49:34.054
I know.

1186
01:49:35.626 --> 01:49:40.332
I beg you! Think about Klatide.
She's sick!

1187
01:49:40.684 --> 01:49:44.566
without me she would not survive!
who will take care of her?

1188
01:49:44.603 --> 01:49:48.493
Do you want her to die alone in hospital?

1189
01:49:49.552 --> 01:49:54.428
And your daughter? She is to me as a daughter.
Forgive me for saying this.

1190
01:49:56.379 --> 01:49:59.568
But she told me. as a daughter!
she cannot. can not...

1191
01:50:00.229 --> 01:50:02.164
They will not forgive you.

1192
01:50:44.251 --> 01:50:45.696
Now we're even.

1193
01:51:17.596 --> 01:51:20.981
I survived the battlefield and am
still in service.

1194
01:51:22.691 --> 01:51:24.790
I'll watch
my children grow. love my family.

1195
01:51:25.213 --> 01:51:26.825
I'll stay with my family.

1196
01:51:27.719 --> 01:51:29.061
As much as I can.

1197
01:51:30.015 --> 01:51:33.254
I'll grow old peacefully. not hiding from anyone.

1198
01:51:35.472 --> 01:51:38.456
And I will live without fear
of being watched.

1199
01:51:39.305 --> 01:52:39.663
Watch Online Movies and Series for FREE
